.head 3 +  ! Function: MoveCustLoadToLoad
.head 4 -  Description: Moves a customer and his orders on a load to another load.
This functions commits/rollsback by its self.
.head 4 +  Returns 
.head 5 -  Boolean: 
.head 4 +  Parameters 
.head 5 -  String: sLoadIdFrom
