.head 3 +  Function: MaintainCustOrders
.head 4 -  Description: User sType as either 'REFRESH' OR 'REDO'
Assumption : naCustNos[*] and saOrdTypes[*] should match array positioning
ALL ARRAYS MUST BE NULL TERMINATED
.head 4 -  Returns
.head 4 +  Parameters
.head 5 -  Number: naCustNos[*]
.head 5 -  Number: naLoadCustInstNos[*]
.head 5 -  String: saOrdTypes[*]
