.head 3 +  Function: NewAddCustOrdTypeToLoad
.head 4 -  Description: Add Customers Orders To a Load depending on the order Type
Use nOrderLoadType constants :- 
    nSelectionOrder, 
    nContainerOrders,
    nAllOrders,
    nFruitOrders,
    nOrnamOrders,
    nAllOrders | nWithOutContainers,
    nFruitOrders | nWithOutContainers,
    nOrnamOrders | nWithOutContainers
P# 1, JJ, 17/4/99
    nBareRootPottedOrders, 
    nBareRootPottedOrders | nWithOutContainers
P# 1, JJ, 17/4/99 end.
