.head 5 +  Function: fnGetPlantsPlusCustomers
.head 6 -  Description: This function checks to see if any of the customers that are on this load or selected are plants plus referral customers and if there are any then it prints out a report exactly the same as COD.

It scrolls through each row in the customer table and uses the customer ID to check if they are a plant plus referral customer.

If they are , the customer number is added to a comma separated string which is then passed to a dialog

