.head 3 +  Function: ResetCustBarcodeFlag
.head 4 -  Description: Resets the Customer_Order table Barcodes_Printed flag For Customer No
This function does its own commit and rollbacks
.head 4 +  Returns
.head 5 -  Boolean:
.head 4 +  Parameters
.head 5 -  String: sLoadId
.head 5 -  Number: nCustNo
.head 5 -  Number: nInstNo
