.head 6 -  Description:
.head 6 +  Returns
.head 7 -  Boolean:
.head 6 +  Parameters
.head 7 -  Number: nLocationId
.head 7 -  Receive String: sFarmName
.head 7 -  Receive Number: nRowNo
.head 7 -  Receive Number: nSeqNo
